  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, combine lemon juice, garlic, ginger, paprika, cumin, coriander, and cayenne pepper.",
    "Add the pork cubes and marinate for at least 2 hours or overnight.",
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread the marinated pork, onions, and bell peppers onto skewers.",
    "Brush the skewers with olive oil and season with salt.",
    "Grill the kebabs for 8-10 minutes per side, or until the pork is cooked through.",
    "Serve hot and garnish with fresh parsley."
